graph LR
    %% Top level user access
    Users[Users/Data Teams] -->|HTTPS| Browser[Web Browser]
    Browser -->|Access| Frontend
    
    %% Databricks App Layer
    Frontend[Next.js Frontend<br/>React 19 + MUI v7] -->|HTTP/SSE| Backend[FastAPI Backend<br/>Multi-Agent System]
    
    %% Backend to Platform
    Backend -->|Python Client| SDK[Databricks SDK]
    Backend -->|State| Lakebase[(Lakebase<br/>Postgres-compatible)]
    Backend -->|Config| UCTables[(UC Tables<br/>Metadata)]
    Backend -->|LLM| ModelServing[Model Serving<br/>LLM Endpoints]
    
    %% SDK to Workspace
    SDK -->|Query/Job/UC APIs| Workspace[Workspace APIs]
    
    %% Workspace to Data
    Workspace -->|Query Analysis| QueryHistory[SQL Query History]
    Workspace -->|Job Analysis| JobRuns[Job Metadata]
    Workspace -->|Governance| UCMetadata[UC Lineage]
    Workspace -->|FinOps| BillingData[System Tables<br/>Usage/Cost]
    
    %% External LLM
    ModelServing -.->|Proxy| LLMProvider[LLM Provider<br/>OpenAI/Azure]
    Backend -.->|Optional Fallback| LLMProvider
    Backend -.->|Optional| Redis[(Redis Cache)]
    
